      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities conducted on the same device geometry, fluid, and operating conditions as the COU; experimental data cover the full COU operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "All validation activities were numerical simulations. The single published experimental comparison used a geometrically similar but distinct pump. Relevance of validation activities to the COU is therefore low; achieved level 2 vs required level 5. The team narrative argues the simulation is 'as good as' experiment, but this is not captured in the structured evidence.",
